    "body": "Problem:\r\nMany color schemes assume the Comment hl group is dim text and use it for secondary text, decorations, or parts of UI. This is true for many color schemes but not all.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nIntroducing a new highlight group with a more specific meaning, similar to Underlined or Ignore.\r\n\r\nThe new group links to Comment by default so the behavior is unchanged for color schemes that don't define it.",
    "closed_at": null,
